  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2004-09-15",
    "date": "2004-09-22T19:18:52Z",
    "text": "Close the Bank Examiner Revolving Door Act - Amends the Federal Deposit Insurance Act to prohibit certain former Federal bank examiners and other banking supervisory personnel from holding office, position, or employment at a depository institution during the one-year period following cessation of their Federal service.\n\nMandates forfeiture of Federal retirement and other benefits for violations of this Act.\n\n Requires the head of any Federal banking agency to report such a violation to the Director of the Office of Personnel Management."
  },
